  "3168520": {
    "name": "BloomTale",
    "steam_appid": 3168520,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《BloomTale》的世界里，你将经营属于自己的花店，让创意尽情绽放！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《BloomTale》中的每一朵花都承载着独特的意义。你需要掌握花语的艺术，根据顾客的需求制作花束，同时使鲜花保持鲜活。不仅如此，你还可以倾听顾客的故事，他们的经历就像他们所定制的花束一样，蕴含着丰富的独特情感……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是想在忙碌的一天后放松身心，还是寻求挑战，《BloomTale》都将是你的理想选择。游戏在休闲与趣味之间实现了完美平衡。装饰你的花店，探索每种鲜花背后的意义，尝试多样的花材与装饰，展现你的创造力。完成令顾客满意的花束，让你的花店声名远扬。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168520/extras/694592ca4d8b7df4829d5d6d92564400.avif?t=1770012854\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>店铺管理:</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保持鲜花的鲜活度，合理支配店铺收入，以及预防花朵免遭虫害。持续制作高品质的花束，让顾客满意，确保你的花店生意兴旺。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168520/extras/9729c8fa6ae09ff9ff80aea56daeac0c.poster.avif?t=1770012854\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168520/extras/9729c8fa6ae09ff9ff80aea56daeac0c.webm?t=1770012854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168520/extras/9729c8fa6ae09ff9ff80aea56daeac0c.mp4?t=1770012854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>结识本地居民:</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与形形色色的顾客互动，每位顾客都有ta独特的喜好和背景故事。有些顾客的要求可能会令你大吃一惊，另一些则会为你的日常生活增添一抹神秘色彩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168520/extras/3390ed617c380e7723b4180303841326.poster.avif?t=1770012854\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168520/extras/3390ed617c380e7723b4180303841326.webm?t=1770012854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168520/extras/3390ed617c380e7723b4180303841326.mp4?t=1770012854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发挥创意:</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《BloomTale》中，你可以组合不同颜色和风格的鲜花，设计独具一格的花艺作品。但除了发挥艺术创意外，你还需要懂得具有深厚传统的各种花语。它们是游戏的重要一环，让你能够利用花束传递特定的情感与信息。在满足顾客需求的同时，融入你的个人风格，为每一束花赋予独特的意义与故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>装饰花束:</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了鲜花以外，还可以用各类宝石、丝带和多彩多样的包装纸来点缀你的花束，让你的作品更加独特、精致！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168520/extras/31b908fac458f11ce2ba37aa896a3e0a.poster.avif?t=1770012854\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168520/extras/31b908fac458f11ce2ba37aa896a3e0a.webm?t=1770012854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168520/extras/31b908fac458f11ce2ba37aa896a3e0a.mp4?t=1770012854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>花材收集:</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中共有超过50种独特的花材供你使用，以创作属于你的美丽花束！随着花店等级的提升，你还会解锁更多品种的鲜花。查看游戏内的花语指南，深入了解每种花卉的独特意义，并将它们运用到花束制作中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168520/extras/8fc20bc860b85b8f106135ec0b694492.poster.avif?t=1770012854\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168520/extras/8fc20bc860b85b8f106135ec0b694492.webm?t=1770012854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168520/extras/8fc20bc860b85b8f106135ec0b694492.mp4?t=1770012854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>装饰店铺:</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用各种家具、饰品和花盆装饰你的店铺，打造个性化的室内环境，展现你的独特风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168520/extras/331d99381e718a77c9f954dc22374718.poster.avif?t=1770012854\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168520/extras/331d99381e718a77c9f954dc22374718.webm?t=1770012854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168520/extras/331d99381e718a77c9f954dc22374718.mp4?t=1770012854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
